{"tid":1659852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國證監會凍結18名交易員資產　主要來自中國","createTime":"2019-10-17T07:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T08:31:37.000Z","uid":152123,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e55287ec621974854d72e346d3a11746469243","tid":1659852,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"美國證券交易委員會凍結18名交易員的資產，他們主要來自中國，涉嫌國際市場操縱，數年來非法獲利超過3100萬美元。美國證監會說，這些交易員操縱逾3000隻美國上市證券，歷時最少6年。他們涉嫌在多家經紀公司以他人名義開設百多個帳戶以操縱股價，製造虛假交易牟利。證監會相信操作仍然持續。當局表示，被告在知情或無意中不知情的情況下參與證券欺詐計劃，有關交易員多次收到經紀商對他們的操縱性交易發出的警告。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2019-10-17 15:19:20"},{"pid":"df775b364a0d880b4b75fbc45e95309e0daba5f3","tid":1659852,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:28:25.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"d12b397e3bb7e1db010a4309bcc0fbed3951a291","tid":1659852,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769d69a5aca42d68a37b5ba43c1a8f9ac4cdaec6","tid":1659852,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"大家記得要響twitter 同美國講條bill好重要<br />\n條Bill 未過參議院架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n唔該去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n然後講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#hongkonghumanrightsanddemocracyact <br />\n#standwithhongkong<br />\n#fightforfreedom<br />\n<br />\n留意番Representatives 同Senator係有分別，<br />\n望清楚其他人點叫人先好！<br />\n唔好叫人First Name！<br />\n外媒報條Bill 的新聞都好重要！<br />\nretweet哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg